{
  "stem": "95.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it's freezing, freezing cold, snow up to your knees, and all we had is a very light striped uniforms.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We all took blankets and put it over our shoulders to have some warm there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, my three friends, the Fogels and the father-- and their father, they knew that if this father walked, they're not going to make it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they hid under the barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were not liquidated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were liberated by the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They went in France.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were there in February 1945, they arrived back in France.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And somehow, they tell some of the people that I was alive at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But we walked-- like everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Like all survivors, like everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We walked for days and days in deep snow, and there's not enough food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We have 4,000 people, SS on each side with guns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Their order was, you sit when you're not supposed to, you cannot walk anymore, you have to be killed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they kept those orders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we walking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I'm there with a friend now that I made in Blechhammer, a very nice man.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We're walking in front of the line, and we keep ourselves alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then again, unbelievable thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "When we would find a barn, if they found a barn that's big enough to-- so, for like three hours, we would sleep on the-- on the straw.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And when we would do that, I would escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I would go out of the barn when everybody was asleep, go to a farm and ask, please give me a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they would do that, give me a glass of milk, a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
